WEBVTT



00:00:11.168 --> 00:00:12.352
I'm Derek Walker.

00:00:12.512 --> 00:00:14.432
And I'm excited today to take a look at the

00:00:14.080 --> 00:00:18.144
To introduce you to my book, Live Long and Strong.

00:00:18.208 --> 00:00:22.304
God's keys to long life and youth renewal.

00:00:22.784 --> 00:00:24.960
You know we all want along

00:00:24.736 --> 00:00:27.008
And a satisfying life, don't we?

00:00:27.104 --> 00:00:31.488
But did you know that God's God also wants you?

00:00:31.296 --> 00:00:32.928
To live long

00:00:32.864 --> 00:00:34.496
And to live strong.

00:00:35.328 --> 00:00:41.568
Very few people are aware that there are promises from God on the subject of living a long life.

00:00:41.536 --> 00:00:46.880
Although there's much teaching on divine healing, there's very little on living in divine health.

00:00:47.072 --> 00:00:50.944
In my book, Live Long and Strong, I address this lack.

00:00:50.656 --> 00:00:57.600
providing what I believe is the first in-depth study of all that the Bible has to say on living a long life.

00:00:57.920 --> 00:01:01.216
God wants you to live long and strong

00:01:01.184 --> 00:01:03.776
His promise in Psalm ninety one.

00:01:03.936 --> 00:01:10.176
And in fact, I do a whole chapter on Psalm 91. But verse 16, he says, "With long life..."

00:01:09.888 --> 00:01:13.728
I will satisfy him and show him my salvation.

00:01:13.536 --> 00:01:23.584
And Jesus said in John 10:10, "I have come that they may have life and have it in abundance, and that's not just quality of life, but quantity of life, not just any

00:01:23.104 --> 00:01:25.408
in eternity. But right now,

00:01:25.568 --> 00:01:26.944
But God says:

00:01:26.784 --> 00:01:35.936
My people are destroyed for lack of knowledge. You see, if you don't know God's word on a subject, you won't have the faith to receive his promises.

00:01:35.616 --> 00:01:37.792
Of long life, in this case.

00:01:37.568 --> 00:01:44.448
And so in this book I introduce you to the wealth of Scripture that promises you long life.

00:01:44.224 --> 00:01:54.272
In the appendix in the back, I have a whole list of long life scriptures and long life confessions. We talk about things that will shorten your life and things that will lengthen your life.

00:01:53.792 --> 00:01:55.104
Lengthen your life.

00:01:54.944 --> 00:02:02.464
We talk about issues such as martyrdom and what about those who die young? how do we handle that?

00:02:02.432 --> 00:02:05.376
we talk about fighting for your life.

00:02:05.376 --> 00:02:10.752
Because fighters have a longer life, so we're going to put fight in you.

00:02:10.688 --> 00:02:20.736
and we'll also talk about the renewal of youth, how to receive that and wonderful examples of the great men of God who received the renewal of their youth.

00:02:20.256 --> 00:02:27.008
Why do we need long life? Not selfishly, but so that we can fulfill the will of God.

00:02:26.656 --> 00:02:36.704
for our lives. So I recommend to you that you order a copy of this book because it will lengthen your life and it will strengthen your life.

00:02:36.224 --> 00:02:37.376
In your life.
